  "description": {
   "en": "Men are servants of knowledge.  \n  \nThe Sorcerers' Guild was no more… The guild possessed many dangerous grimoires, worshipped pure magic.  \nThe guild was condemned as a terrorist organization. A chivalric order of scientists was formed, hunting it down.  \nOne after another, the sorcerers were captured, executed. Gradually, the guild lost its power. Eventually, they declared disbandment.  \nThe remaining sorcerers were scattered across the world, marked as dangerous, forced to live as wanted criminals.  \n  \nSpectral Wizard was among them…"
  },
